parameters:
Salaryman: I have arrived. This is the location
for today's business meeting.
Oh, it's farther than I thought...

Salaryman: Is that so? It's actually closer than
usual... A-anyway, please support me as I proceed
with the negotiations based on the contents of the
documents.

Yes, I think I can be of some help, even if it's
just a little.

Salaryman: ...I'm usually alone, so just having
someone with me is appreciated... Alright, let's
go.

Salaryman: It's already gotten to this time...!
But, we were able to successfully complete the
contract! Thank you very much!

Salaryman: By the way, Nagatsuki-san, you're
really good at sales!

Salaryman: I've never seen the director smile like
that before... It's the first time for me...

Because it's important to be liked by the other
person, I prioritized getting along first.

Salaryman: W-Well, that's true... but how did you
know that the director's hobby is golf?

The director's watch is a golf watch, and when I
saw his hands, there were octopus-like marks as if
he had been practicing swings, so I thought that
might be it.

Salaryman: I see... That's helpful...! Um... Could
you please teach me various sales techniques?!
Yes, if it's something I know.

Salaryman: Thank you very much! Well then... \.\.
Shall we head home for now?
